# Pre-Commit Workflow

**CRITICAL**: Before committing any changes, you MUST run and pass all three checks.

## Quick Command (All Checks)

```bash
bun run lint:fix && bun run typecheck && bun test
```

## Required Checks

### 1. Lint Check - Code style and linting

```bash
bun run lint        # Check only
bun run lint:fix    # Auto-fix issues
bun run lint:unsafe # Unsafe auto-fix
```

### 2. TypeScript Check - Type safety

```bash
bun run typecheck         # Check types
bun run typecheck:watch   # Watch mode
```

### 3. Tests - Functionality

```bash
bun test              # Run all tests
bun test --watch      # Watch mode
```

## CI Workflows

These checks run automatically in GitHub Actions:
- **Lint** - Linting and formatting
- **TypeScript Type Check** - Type safety
- **Tests** - All tests must pass

**Never commit code that fails any of these checks.**

